name: Cell Lab Design File
summary: Learn about .GENOME files and view a list of programs that open them.

content: Cell Lab comes with 45 challenges where you must design an organism that can survive a particular environment. And as you solve challenges, you unlock new genes that will give cells new properties. You can also play an experimental mode where you set the parameters of the environment then test your organism you designed to see if it thrives or dies.
